author: Debbie Jamieson
title: People trapped in two car crash near Queenstown
text:
People trapped in two car crash near Queenstown DEBBIE JAMIESON Last updated 14:54, February 13 2017 
A helicopter is flying from Dunedin to the scene of a two car head on crash near Queenstown. 
A police spokeswoman said it appeared people were trapped following the crash about 2.30pm on the Gibbston Highway. 
Ambulance, police and fire brigade are at the scene. 
More details to follow.
